@startuml
title Redis 会话记忆存储 - 数据可视化

database "Redis 服务器\n127.0.0.1:8379" as RedisSrv
rectangle "Redis Key: default\nType: List | Length: 168" as KeyInfo
rectangle "消息列表 (LRANGE default 0 -1)" as MsgList {
  rectangle "#1  USER: 你好" as M1
  rectangle "#2  ASSISTANT: 你好！很高兴为你服务！..." as M2
  rectangle "#3  USER: 今天天气怎么样" as M3
  rectangle "#4  ASSISTANT: 看起来IP定位暂时出了点小问题..." as M4
  rectangle "#5  USER: 世界上最好的编程语言是什么" as M5
  rectangle "#6  ASSISTANT: 没有绝对的最好..." as M6
  rectangle "... (共168条, 截取前6条)" as M7
}

RedisSrv --> KeyInfo
KeyInfo --> MsgList

M1 -[hidden]-> M2
M2 -[hidden]-> M3
M3 -[hidden]-> M4
M4 -[hidden]-> M5
M5 -[hidden]-> M6
M6 -[hidden]-> M7

note right of MsgList
  问题分析：
  conversationId 写死为 "default"
  -> 所有用户共享同一会话
  
  后果：
  1. 用户A的问题和回答混入用户B的上下文
  2. 长期累积导致 token 超限
  3. 无法隔离不同用户的会话
  
  修复方案：
  DeepseekChatClient.java:38
  .advisors(a -> a.param(
    ChatMemory.CONVERSATION_ID,
    userId  改为动态值
  ))
end note

@enduml
